persistence.file.text

Class EntityIterator<T extends Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • persistence.file.text.EntityIterator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.util.Iterator<T>

    public class EntityIterator<T extends Entity>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    EntityIterator represents a pointer to an open file with a collection of entity. EntityIterator lazily loads Entity matching the given predicate, ensuring that unused entity will not be loaded in the process. Close this EntityIterator when not in use to prevent a resource leak.
    Author:
    YingHao
